The Pantone To Go Cup, goes anywhere! Colorful and fun, this no nonsense no spill cup has an easy turnstile top that controls the flow of the liquid. The To Go cup has a Thermo effect (double walled) and will keep hot liquids warm for 4 hours and cold beverages cool for 8 hours. This is a great gift for those always on the go! Go in color with Pantone To Go Cups.

